rk Theme. The Editor Theme setting is located in the right column at Appearance &#62; Custom CSS.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/dark-theme-now-available-in-siteorigin-css/\">Dark Theme Now Available in SiteOrigin CSS</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1437:\"<p>SiteOrigin CSS version <code>1.5.0</code> includes an editor theme option. Choose between the default Light theme or switch to a Dark Theme.</p>\n<p>The Editor Theme setting is located in the right column at <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Appearance</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Custom CSS</span></span>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_349371\" style=\"width: 375px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-349371\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/editor-theme-setting.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"355\" height=\"266\" class=\"size-full wp-image-349371\" style=\"max-width: 355px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-349371\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Switch editor themes using the setting in the right column at Appearance > Custom CSS.</p></div>\n<p>If you have any queries or requests, please, let us know. Free support is available on the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/thread/\">SiteOrigin forum</a>. Quick email support with a wide scope is available <a href=\"mailto:support@siteorigin.com\">via email</a> for all SiteOrigin Premium users.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/dark-theme-now-available-in-siteorigin-css/\">Dark Theme Now Available in SiteOrigin CSS</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://siteorigin.com/dark-theme-now-available-in-siteorigin-css/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"WPML Translation Editor – Page Builder Compatibility\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 01 Dec 2021 13:27:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=342053\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:544:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce that Page Builder is now compatible with the WPML Advanced Translation Editor. Translate your SiteOrigin Page Builder and Widgets Bundle content quickly and easily using the Automatic Translation option or manually translating the available strings.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/\">WPML Translation Editor &#8211; Page Builder Compatibility</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5184:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce that Page Builder is now compatible with the <a href=\"https://wpml.org/?aid=88702&amp;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\">WPML Advanced Translation Editor</a>. Translate your SiteOrigin Page Builder and Widgets Bundle content quickly and easily using the Automatic Translation option or manually translating the available strings.</p>\n<p><em>WPML&#8217;s Advanced Translation Editor allows you and your translators to work more quickly and easily while providing better translations. The editor comes with key features like machine translation, a glossary, translation memory, spell checker, HTML-less editing, and more.</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/translating-your-contents/advanced-translation-editor/?aid=88702&amp;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\">Find out more about the WPML Advanced Translation Editor</a>.</p>\n<h3>Translating SiteOrigin Page Builder Pages Using WPML&#8217;s Translation Editor</h3>\n<p>Navigate to the page or post you&#8217;d like to translate. Locate the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Language</span></span> meta box in the right column. With the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Use WPML&#8217;s Translation Editor</span></span> option enabled, click on the plus icon corresponding to the language you&#8217;d like to translate.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_341935\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-341935\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-341935 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1366\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-300x160.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-699x373.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-768x410.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-1536x820.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-2048x1093.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-1050x560.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/language-meta-box-313x167.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-341935\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click on the plus icon corresponding to the language you&#8217;d like to translate.</p></div>\n<p>Use the WPML Translation Editor to translate the page content, either automatically using the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Translate automatically</span></span> button or manually. Click the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Complete</span></span> button when you&#8217;re done.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_342233\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-342233\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1253\" class=\"size-full wp-image-342233\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-300x147.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-699x342.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-768x376.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-1536x752.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-2048x1003.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-1050x514.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/wpml-advanced-translation-editor-313x153.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-342233\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">WPML Translation Editor interface.</p></div>\n<h3>Links</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder/compatible-translation-plugins/using-page-builder-wpml/\">SiteOrigin Documentation: Using Page Builder with WPML</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/using-wpml-siteorigin/?aid=88702&amp;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPML Documentation: Using WPML with SiteOrigin Page Builder</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading. We hope you find the enhanced SiteOrigin &#8211; WPML integration useful. If you have any queries or comments, please, let us know below. If you&#8217;re a SiteOrigin Premium user, please, email <a href=\"mailto:support@siteorigin.com\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">support@siteorigin.com</a> as queries arise.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/\">WPML Translation Editor &#8211; Page Builder Compatibility</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://siteorigin.com/wpml-translation-editor-page-builder-compatibility/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"Link an entire Page Builder row, cell, or widget with the Link Overlay Addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://siteorigin.com/link-an-entire-page-builder-row-cell-or-widget-with-the-link-overlay-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:106:\"https://siteorigin.com/link-an-entire-page-builder-row-cell-or-widget-with-the-link-overlay-addon/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 21 Nov 2021 09:31:31 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=337527\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:516:\"<p>We\'re thrilled to announce the Link Overlay Addon recently introduced in SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.27.0</code>. The Link Overlay Addon allows easy linking of any Page Builder row, cell, or widget.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/link-an-entire-page-builder-row-cell-or-widget-with-the-link-overlay-addon/\">Link an entire Page Builder row, cell, or widget with the Link Overlay Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7644:\"<div id=\"pl-337527\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-337527-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-337527-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-337527-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>We\'re thrilled to announce the Link Overlay Addon recently introduced in SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.27.0</code>. The Link Overlay Addon allows easy linking of any Page Builder row, cell, or widget.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-337527-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-337527-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-337527-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h3>Usage Example - Linking a Page Builder Row</h3>\n<p>Edit the row you\'d like to link by clicking the wrench icon followed by <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Edit Row</span></span>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1876\" height=\"326\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-336422\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row.png 1876w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-300x52.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-699x121.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-768x133.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-1536x267.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-1050x182.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/edit-page-builder-row-313x54.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1876px) 100vw, 1876px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, locate and open the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Link Overlay</span></span> settings section.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"580\" height=\"1046\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-336421\" style=\"max-width: 290px\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2.png 580w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2-166x300.png 166w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2-388x699.png 388w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/row-styles-link-overlay-2-313x564.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 580px) 100vw, 580px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>URL</strong><br />\nEnter the URL you\'d like to link the row to. For example, to link the row to SiteOrigin.com, enter <code>https://siteorigin.com</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Open link in new window</strong><br />\nEnable to open the link in a new browser window.</p>\n<p>The process is very similar for linking a <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/link-overlay/#heading-linking-a-page-builder-cell\">cell</a> or <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/link-overlay/#heading-linking-a-page-builder-widget\">widget</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-337527-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><